Annah Namiriano mupepepeti mukuru webepanhau rinobuda mazuva ese reJuba Monito akaudza sangano reSouth Sudan in Focus kuti, 'Pakati paNdira naKurume, vashandi mubazi rezvekuchengetedzwa kwenyika vakabvisa zvizvinyorwa zvenhau zvakawanda kubva mubepanhau.
