Nhau dzakange dziri pamusoro pechiitiko ichi dzakange dzanyorwa nebepanhau reJuba Monitor dzakabviswa nevashandi vemubazi rekuchengetedzwakwenyika bepanhau rava pamushina wekudhinda.
