Chimwezve chikepembozha chemutsigiri wehutongi hweRussia chakatorwa nemusi weChina
Vakumbirwa neUnited States, vakuru vemu Fiji vakatora chikepembozha chinokosha mari inoita mazana matatu emamiriyoni chaSuleiman Kerimov, bazi rezvemutemo rataura kudaro.Vakuru vanoti chikepembozha ichi chiri kuLautoka muFiji makare.
Chikepembozha chaKerimov, chinonzi Amadea, chiine ruvara rwemureza weCayman Island, chinoonzi changa chiri muFiji kubva mwedzi wakapfuura, mushure chabva kuMexico.
Magweta ari kumiririra muridzi wacho anoti mudziyo uyu ndewe mumwe mutsigiri wehutongi wemuRussia.
Kerimov akanga atemwa nezvirango zvehupfumi ne U.S. muna 2014 nemuna 2018 nekuda kwezvakaitwa neRussia muSyria nemuUkraine.
European Union yakamurovawo nezvirango zvehupfumi.
Muna Kurume, hurumende yeU.S. yakazivisa chirongwa chakasimba chekutsvaga nekutora zvinhu zvinokosha zvezvinoto zveku Russian zvanga zvichitsigira hurumende yavaVladmir Putin, sechikamu chekupindura zvakaitwa neRussia payakapinda nechisimba munyika yeUkraine.
Chirongwa ichi chiri kutungamirirwa neBazi rezvemutemo, rinodaidzwa kunzi Chikwata Chekubvutira Vanotonga Nechisimba kana kuti Task Force KleptoCapture.
Muchuchusi mukuru weU.S., Merrick Garland akatura mashoko nemusi weChina ekuti "hapana nzvimbo yekuhwanda yezvinokosha zvezvigeven'a zvinogonesa nekutsigira hutungamiriri hweRussia kuita mabasa awo.
Akatiwo zvakare, "Bazi Rezvemutemo harisi kuzoneta mubasa redu rekuona kuti avo vari kutsigira nekugonesa kupondwa kwevanhu neparadzwa kwenyika kwatiri kuona kuUkraine vazvidavirira pamberi pemutemo."
Muna Kubvumbi, vakurudzirwa neU.S., vakuru vemuSpain vakabvuta chikepembozha chechinoto chekuRussia chinonzi Viktor Vekselberg, muridzi wemubatanidzwa wemakambani makuru ekuRussia anodaidzwa kuti Renova Group.
Svondo rakapera, dare revamiririri reU.S. House of Representatives rakatendera danho raizotendera hurumende yeU.S. kuti itengese nzvimbo nezvivakwa zvakatorerwa zvinoto zvekuRussia zvinokosha mari inodarika mamiriyoni maviri emadhora, mari yacho igobatsira Ukraine.
