Dare Repamusoro remuMyanmar Rinokandira Kunze Chikumbiro Cha Aung San Suu Kyi Kuti Nyaya Dzaarikupomerwa Dzehuori Dzitarisiswezve
Chikumbiro chemutungamiriri we Myanmar uyo akabviswa pachigaro, Aung San Suu Kyi chekuongororwazve kwekutongerwa kugara mujeri kwemakore mashanu chakarambwa neChitatu nedare repamuso remunyika iyi.
Kutonga kwedare uku kunonzi kwakaturwa mapepa ekuti nyaya iyi iongororwe achangounzwa, uye dare iri rakaramba kunzwa zvachose zvaitaurwa nevachuchusi vehurumende nemagweta aSuu Kyi.
Amai Suu Kyi, vane makore makumi manomwe nematanhatu vakatongwa svondo rakapera mushure mekuwanikwa vaine mhosva gumi neimwe dzehuori, kusanganisira kutambira mari yefufuro nemagodo egorodhe ane hukoshi hunodarika zviuru mazana matanhatu emadhora.
Gweta ravo rakati kupomerwa uku hakuna musoro.
Amai Suu Kyi vakange vatotongerwa kugara mujeri kwemakore matanhatu nekuda kwezvakaita zvekudzivisa mauto, kutyora mitemo yekudzivirira kupararira kwedenda reCOVID-19 uye nekutyora mitemo yezvekushandisa mishina yekutaura nevamwe yakaita sedzinhare, nharembozha nemapotonjere.
Vachiri vakatarisana nedzimwe mhosva dzavari kupomerwa, uye kana vakawanikwa vaine mhosva vanogona kutongerwa kugara mujeri kwemakore anodarika zana nemakumi mashanu.
Amai Suu Kyi vanga vari musungwa anenge akachengetedzwa ari mumba make kubva mauto zvaakavabvutira masimba ekutonga gore rakapfuura.
Kubva mauto abvuta masimba ekutonga musi wa 1 Kukadzi 2021, kwese kwese munyika manga muune kuratidzira nekushora hurumende yechiuto iyi.
Hurumende iyi yakabva yatsikirira zvine chinya kuratidzira uku, izvo zvakasita magari vemunyika iyi vanopfuura chiuru nemazana masere vafa nemwe vanodarika zviuru gumi vasungwa, vachipomerwa mhosva kana kuti vawanikwa vaine mhosva, sekutaurwa kwazvakaitwa- nesangano rinobatsira vasungwa vezvematongerwo rekuBurma, Assistance Association for Political Prisoners (Burma).
